Package: scriptorium
Title: Easily Install and Load the 'Vellum' Graphics Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Schoch", , "david.schoch@cynkra.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'vellum' ecosystem is a set of packages for drawing in R
    that share a scene model and a common design: 'vellum' (a low-level
    graphics backend with a Rust engine), 'quill' (a pipe-first grammar of
    graphics on top of it), and 'gloss' (client-side interactive HTML
    widgets for the scenes they produce). 'scriptorium' is a meta-package
    that installs and loads them together, in the spirit of the
    'tidyverse'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://schochastics.github.io/scriptorium/,
    https://github.com/schochastics/scriptorium
